                <h5>Which Process Is Better?</h5>
                <p>Honestly speaking, neither process is technically better than the other. You don’t need to worry about whether an HPHT diamond is better than a CVD diamond. In fact, when it comes to diamonds, the process doesn’t really matter. Whether you’ve picked a natural diamond, an HPHT diamond or a CVD diamond, what you get is a truly magnificent stone that will last forever.</p>
